Experiment 2 of Power Electronics Laboratory for 6th Semester Electrical Engineering UG Students.

Title - Single Phase Full Wave Center-Tapped Rectifier

Specifications :-
Input voltage: 230 V, 50 Hz, single phase AC supply; rectifier is fed through a single phase
transformer with centre-tapped secondary; turns ratio- primary : secondary-1 : secondary-2 = 2 : 1 : 1. 

Triggering Angle set for 30 degrees
Loads - Purely Resistive, RL, RLE loads
                 
